Each folder and their intended use:

      • assets: Images, fonts, etc…
      • components: Presentational/reusable components
      • config: Configuration of the app (constants, colors)
      • navigation: React Navigation settings and navigators
      • screens (AKA containers): Smart components that handles the logic of the app
      • services: Wrappers on API calls to external servicess
      • utils: Reusable utilities
      • context: Use to store data which will be global to the React components
                 e.g. Current Authenticated user or Theme
      • dev: Tester components

Requesting permission to Access Location
      • Code located under android/app/src/main/AndriodManifest.xml